      "text": "Research how Aider (AI coding CLI) stores its coding sessions. I need to know:\n1. Where the session data is stored (file path, database location)\n2. What format it uses (SQLite, JSON, JSONL, etc.)\n3. The schema/structure of the session data\n4. What fields are available (messages, tool calls, file edits, timestamps)\n\nSearch the web for \"Aider CLI session storage format\" and \"Aider chat history format\". Also check the Aider GitHub repo for documentation about session storage.\n\nReturn a detailed summary of the storage format, file paths, and schema.",
