      "text": "The user wants to understand how Aider (an AI coding CLI tool) stores its coding sessions. I need to research:\n1. Where session data is stored (file path, database location)\n2. What format it uses (SQLite, JSON, JSONL, etc.)\n3. The schema/structure of the session data\n4. What fields are available (messages, tool calls, file edits, timestamps)\n\nI'll start by searching the web for information about Aider session storage format, then check the GitHub repo for documentation.",
